### 1. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8091/api/health

### 2. 上传文档
POST http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"

这是一个测试文档的内容。
电力设备运行规程中规定，变压器油温异常时应立即检查冷却系统。

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

{"专业":"电力"}
--boundary123--

### 3. 文档列表
GET http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents?page=1&pageSize=20

### 4. 文档详情（替换为你的文档ID）
GET http://localhost:8091/api/documents/2b5f269c6e9f44f48dda1dca5bf5c42f

### 5. 查看切片
GET http://localhost:8091/api/documents/2b5f269c6e9f44f48dda1dca5bf5c42f/chunks?page=1&pageSize=50

### 6. 下载文档
GET http://localhost:8091/api/documents/2b5f269c6e9f44f48dda1dca5bf5c42f/download

### 7. 更新标签
PUT http://localhost:8091/api/documents/2b5f269c6e9f44f48dda1dca5bf5c42f/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tags": {
    "专业": "电力",
    "设备": "变压器"
  }
}

### 8. 删除文档
DELETE http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents/2b5f269c6e9f44f48dda1dca5bf5c42f

### 9. 批量删除
POST http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents/batch-delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": ["文档ID1", "文档ID2"]
}

### 10. 重试处理
POST http://localhost:8091/api/documents/2b5f269c6e9f44f48dda1dca5bf5c42f/retry
